Marie-José Nat https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie-Jos%C3%A9_Nat 0 Marie-José Benhalassa (born 22 April 1940), known professionally as Marie-José Nat, is a French actress. In 1974, She received a Cannes Film Festival Award for Best Actress for her performance in the film Violins at the Ball.
